'''Victoria Beynon-Cole'''  is a New Zealand extras casting coordinator and actress. She portrayed [[Orcs]], Goblins, [[Uruk-hai]] and [[Nazgûl|Ringwraiths]] in the ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring]]'' and one or more Orcs in ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers]]''. She also was the extras casting director for ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King]]'', ''[[The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey]]'' and the second episode ([[Adrift]]) of ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power]]''.
